  <body>
    <h1>
      Quartic oscillator
    </h1>
    A bead may move without friction along a horizontal rod, while tied to two 
    symmetric springs, as shown in the figure. The unit length is set to the 
    distance between the rod and the fixed point of each spring, which has 
    proper length <i>L</i>.
  </body>
</html>

