  <body>
    <h2>
      Activities
    </h2>
    <ol>
      <li>
        Study analytically the number and stability of the equilibrium points 
        in the following three cases:

        <ul>
          <li>
            <i>L</i> &lt; 1
          </li>
          <li>
            <i>L</i> = 1
          </li>
          <li>
            <i>L</i> &gt; 1
          </li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>
        Sketch the phase-space in each case.
      </li>
      <li>
        Use the simulation to check your answers and drawings.
      </li>
    </ol>
  </body>
</html>

